Resource Profile: Perfil Paciente Cardio

Official URL: https://rme.hl7chile.cl/StructureDefinition/PacienteCardio Version: 0.9
Active as of 2022-12-20 Computable Name: PacienteCardio

Indica datos administrativos del paciente que se encuentra dentro del programa cardiovascular

Usage:

  • This Resource Profile is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide
